Package de.agilecoders.wicket.markup.html.bootstrap.behavior

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CssClassNameProvider
    The CssClassNameProvider provides an interface to abstract the styling of a component and the rendering of the class attribute.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssertTagNameBehavior
    The AssertTagNameBehavior asserts that one of a list of given tag names to be present.
    BootstrapBaseBehavior
    The BootstrapBaseBehavior renders the current active ITheme which includes the BootstrapCssReference and the BootstrapResponsiveCssReference if enabled to the response.
    BootstrapJavascriptBehavior
    The BootstrapJavascriptBehavior renders the BootstrapJavaScriptReference and if active the JqueryPPJavaScriptReference to the response.
    BootstrapResourcesBehavior
    just includes all bootstrap resource references.
    CssClassNameAppender
    A CssClassNameAppender appends the given value, rather than replace it.
    CssClassNameModifier
    A CssClassNameModifier replaces an existing value with the given value.
    CssClassNameRemover
    Removes a value for the CSS class attribute
